ns":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/2760147005/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/2760147005","tinyui":"/x/PYCEp","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=2760147005","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/2760147005/Iniciativas+en+Curso","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/2760147005"}},{"id":"3233218577","type":"page","ari":"ari:cloud:confluence:4e3a1a04-13f1-4674-95f6-44812aec1da3:page/3233218577","base64EncodedAri":"YXJpOmNsb3VkOmNvbmZsdWVuY2U6NGUzYTFhMDQtMTNmMS00Njc0LTk1ZjYtNDQ4MTJhZWMxZGEzOmNvbnRlbnQvMzIzMzIxODU3Nw==","status":"current","title":"VPos","macroRenderedOutput":{},"extensions":{"position":10592077},"_expandable":{"container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","metadata":"","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/history","body":"","version":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN","childTypes":"","schedulePublishInfo":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3233218577/child","ancestors":"","draftVersion":""},"_links":{"self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3233218577","tinyui":"/x/EQC3w","editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3233218577","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3233218577/VPos","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3233218577"}}],"macroRenderedOutput":{},"body":{"storage":{"value":"<table data-table-width=\"760\" data-layout=\"default\" ac:local-id=\"cd53c899-be24-493a-9373-b773650868b8\"><tbody><tr><th><p><strong>Tarea</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Horas</strong></p></th><th><p><strong>Proyecto</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td><p>Crear &lsquo;cajita&rsquo; de vpos 3.0 &lsquo;cybersource&rsquo; en seccion de mis productos en la vista de mis productos (con secci&oacute;n soporte).</p></td><td><p>16hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear la landing (opportunity product) para contratar este nuevo producto vpos 3.0</p><ul><li><p>pendiente logos, precios y &lsquo;landing&rsquo; (textos?) de marketing </p></li></ul></td><td><p>24hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Para la seccion soporte, crear el producto y pasarlo al controller gen&eacute;rico. Simular lo que hoy en d&iacute;a esta para vpos 2.0 pero para el nuevo producto</p></td><td><p>16hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear vista al entrar a la configuracion del nuevo producto vpos 3.0. simular vista redise&ntilde;o nueva de tpago portal (sidebar fija + centro cambiable)</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>crear en men&uacute; sidebar 'Comercios habilitados' &rarr; esta vista mostrar&aacute; una tabla con datos de sucursales del comercio que est&eacute; logueado. Para obtener estos datos consumiremos otro servicio RPG. tambien manejar datos tanto de sandbox como de produccion.</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>crear en men&uacute; sidebar &lsquo;integracion con api&rsquo; &rarr; contendr&aacute; secci&oacute;n para credenciales pub/priv, tanto para sandbox como prod (pesta&ntilde;as switcheables). para obtener estas credenciales consumiremos servicio RPG. Tambien tendr&aacute; una pesta&ntilde;a &lsquo;documentaci&oacute;n&rsquo; con texto,t arjetas de prueba, etc</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>crear en men&uacute; sidebar 'movimientos' &rarr; tabla para filtrar los movimientos hechos con cybersource. consumiremos un dataset de vpos-service para obtener estos datos. la tabla tendra datos de un pago cybersource. ademas, tendr&aacute; filtros sobre los datos numero de boleta, fecha, codigo de autorizacion, medio de pago y sucursal. SOLO SE MOSTRARAN PAGOS CYBERSOURCE APROBADOS. tambi&eacute;n tendra opcion de descargar un .csv con los datos mostrados en la tabla.</p></td><td><p /></td><td><p>commerce-suite</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear endpoint para consumir servicio RPG que obtiene claves pub/priv para comercio cybersource (sandbox y prod)</p></td><td><p>16hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear endpoint para consumir servicio RPG que obtiene comercios habilitados de cybersource para un comercio dado.</p></td><td><p>16hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear endpoint para dataset de nueva tabla cybersource, para el reporte de movimientos. </p></td><td><p>20hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Crear nueva tabla cybersource donde persistir transacciones de cybersource. las columnas ser&aacute;n: nro boleta, transaction id de cybersource, transaction id de commerce service. consulta que otros datos se necesitan para la tabla nueva.</p></td><td><p>4hs</p></td><td><p>commerce-service</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p />","representation":"storage","embeddedContent":[],"_expandable":{"content":"/rest/api/content/3967811698"}},"_expandable":{"editor":"","atlas_doc_format":"","view":"","export_view":"","styled_view":"","dynamic":"","editor2":"","anonymous_export_view":""}},"extensions":{"position":179691879},"_expandable":{"childTypes":"","container":"/rest/api/space/BAN","schedulePublishInfo":"","metadata":"","operations":"","schedulePublishDate":"","children":"/rest/api/content/3967811698/child","restrictions":"/rest/api/content/3967811698/restriction/byOperation","history":"/rest/api/content/3967811698/history","draftVersion":"","descendants":"/rest/api/content/3967811698/descendant","space":"/rest/api/space/BAN"},"_links":{"editui":"/pages/resumedraft.action?draftId=3967811698","webui":"/spaces/BAN/pages/3967811698/Vpos+3.0+cybersource","edituiv2":"/spaces/BAN/pages/edit-v2/3967811698","context":"/wiki","self":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki/rest/api/content/3967811698","tinyui":"/x/cgCA7","collection":"/rest/api/content","base":"https://qubika.atlassian.net/wiki"}}